SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9dc823276f7feafb82ca67662816d1698012dc7","tid":585320,"uid":155084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T16:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我記得係台灣睇既時候 話逆權係韓國票房仲高過與神 <br />\n<br />\n睇左兩次 好撚好睇 最尾個女仔企上巴士到差d喊出黎  但係香港點解唔叫返票名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>原名</blockquote>1987呢套野，我係喺韓國睇，睇試映會，係行內人士先有嘅內部門票。<br />\n睇到馬尿都<span style=\"color: red;\">流</span>撚曬。全場感動。<br />\n香港人未必好感受到，但作為韓國人嚟講，係一段活生生嘅過去。<br />\n<br />\n個陣主演演員都有嚟分享下，打下招呼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/005202_e41355dd11b5f022af28f3902ae78d9d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F005202_e41355dd11b5f022af28f3902ae78d9d.png&h=0d9be1bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/005206_5ae02b7908ecbe15c9aea2c04c3f84ef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F005206_5ae02b7908ecbe15c9aea2c04c3f84ef.png&h=d50eb551&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">流</span>"},{"pid":"d5cff939ed7eec0b882bba810d34ce7bd7ccb30e","tid":585320,"uid":21028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T16:55:21.000Z","msg":"香港人睇戲既水平係咁上下 唔係d咩爆炸武打警匪英雄咁賣座"},{"pid":"0086cebec14bd8ed461ce4f848ac700d2ac17422","tid":585320,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5cff939ed7eec0b882bba810d34ce7bd7ccb30e","tid":585320,"uid":21028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T16:55:21.000Z","msg":"香港人睇戲既水平係咁上下 唔係d咩爆炸武打警匪英雄咁賣座"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T16:59:27.000Z","msg":"其實香港有幾多戲院上逆權公民，又有幾多院上與神同行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac64d7f411acc0c4e7ac0849a6de02e62846f1c","tid":585320,"uid":155084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0086cebec14bd8ed461ce4f848ac700d2ac1742